Package: rexamsconverter
Title: Converts Rmd rexams Files into LaTex format and Backwards
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(person("Vladimir", "Omelyusik", email = "vsomelyusik@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Boris", "Demeshev", email = "boris.demeshev@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut")))
Description: The package contains two main functions. The first one allows you
    to convert formatted LaTex documents into Rmd files which can be 
    processed by the rexams package. The second one does the opposite,
    gathering Rmd files formatted as rexams into the one LaTex document.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    readr (>= 1.2.0),
    stringr (>= 1.3.0),
    exams (>= 2.3-4),
    purrr (>= 0.3.3)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
